      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a purist\u2019s specification, powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine featuring individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing. The drivetrain is anchored by a crisp 6-speed manual gearbox and a factory limited-slip differential, ensuring optimal torque distribution across the rear axle. Critical mechanical milestones have been addressed, including documented rear subframe reinforcement and a comprehensive VANOS overhaul. The suspension geometry remains tight, providing the communicative feedback and lateral stability these chassis are renowned for. While the exterior shows minor signs of road use, the mechanical integrity is excellent, supported by a recent valve clearance adjustment and rod bearing service. This is a driver-focused example that balances raw performance with proven reliability.",
